					<div class="commentbody">what you made is a Shepherd's pie.<br />
<br />
a cottage pie is a meat pie with mash potatoes on top, the key difference is cottage pie's have pastry base and side with no lid topped with potato's, Shepherd's pie's do not have any pastry.</div>
