					<div class="commentsubject">Subject: <span>Really Lazy Cottage Pie</span><br /></div>
					<div class="commentbody">Really lazy cottage pie:<br />
<br />
One can of Mary Kitchen roast beef hash.<br />
One two-serving portion of instant mashed potatoes.<br />
<br />
Layer potatoes over hash, bake until bubbling, then broil for color.<br />
<br />
Serves two hungry people.<br />
<br />
Lazy, simple but darn good.<br />
<br />
Pore ol' John</div>
